We want to create a desigin similar to  **Tensor Processing Unit (TPU)** or **Neural Compute Accelerator (NCA)**. Since "TPU" is strongly associated with Google, I'd use **Tensor Processing Engine (TPE)**.

This gives us a clear identity without tying us to a specific company.

---

# High-Level Vision

The accelerator is designed to accelerate the computational kernels used in modern transformer inference. It acts as a hardware coprocessor that receives commands from host software, fetches tensors from memory, performs computation, and writes results back.

The architecture is intentionally modular so that new compute engines, memory features, and AI capabilities can be added over time.

