```

Eventually, the runtime library could expose APIs like:

```cpp
tensor.matmul(A, B, C);
tensor.relu(C);
tensor.softmax(C);
```

---

# Memory Flow

One of the most important architectural aspects is the movement of data.

```text
DDR Memory

↓

DMA Engine

↓

Local SRAM

↓

Input Buffers

↓

MAC Array

↓

Accumulator

↓

Output Buffer

↓

DMA

↓

DDR
```

The goal is to keep the compute engine busy while DMA transfers the next tiles.

